discovery_rule.name: Jxsjphone game process discovery
discovery_rule.description: 用于自动发现jxsj-phone游戏进程

trigger_prototype.name: {#GAMEPROCESS}产生了新的Coredump文件ON {HOST.NAME}，请注意查看！
{#GAMEPROCESS}产生了新的Coredump文件ON {HOST.NAME}，请注意查看！gdb bt 信息：http://120.92.142.231:8000/jxsj/coredump/core.{ITEM.VALUE1}.txt

trigger_prototype.expression: {Template Game For JxsjPhone Server Formal:logsize[{#GAMEPROCESS}].last()}>2*(({Template Game For JxsjPhone Server Formal:logsize[{#GAMEPROCESS}].last(#2)}+{Template Game For JxsjPhone Server Formal:logsize[{#GAMEPROCESS}].last(#3)}+{Template Game For JxsjPhone Server Formal:logsize[{#GAMEPROCESS}].last(#4)})/3) and {Template Game For JxsjPhone Server Formal:logsize[{#GAMEPROCESS}].last()}>1024000
trigger_prototype.name: {HOST.NAME}上{#GAMEPROCESS}一天产生的日志量过多，请注意查看！

trigger_prototype.expression: ({TRIGGER.VALUE}=0 and {Template Game For JxsjPhone Server Formal:custom.game.process.cpu[{#GAMEPROCESS}].min(15m)}>{$MEDIAHIGH} or {TRIGGER.VALUE}=1 and {Template Game For JxsjPhone Server Formal:custom.game.process.cpu[{#GAMEPROCESS}].min(15m)}>{$MEDIALOW})
trigger_prototype.name: {HOST.NAME}上的{#GAMEPROCESS}进程CPU使用过高，请运维人员查看！
{HOST.NAME}上的{#GAMEPROCESS}进程使用了swap，请注意查看
{HOST.NAME}上的{#GAMEPROCESS}进程已宕，请运维人员确认！
